ithulah {{ subnets, Route-Tables, internet Gateway, NatGateWay }}   -- we can configure all these and create a own n/w

for EG::

oru big organiztion la Dev| TESting | Prod nu 3 environment iurku!!
  if you have to create one VPC in AWS
nama vpc kullah 3 subnet podalam

prod subnet -- intenet gateway attach panalam -- so public facing web appplication vaikalm
Dev subnet -- NatGateway - so private a irunthalum veli internet ku pogamudiyum
Testing subnet -- vpn gateway moolama onpermise n/w connect panalam

during configurin these, security group use pani port open panalam!! 
we can restrict traffic, entha traffic allow panalamnu manage panalam

1, difference between security group & nacl?

securit group - on your EC2 instance la, inbout- outbound traffice ah instance level la managenge panalam
              ithu stateful, means one time inbount traffice if you allowd means, outgoing traffic automatic ah allowd

NACL - subnet level la traffic manage panurathu
      ith stateless, means inboud and outboud ku sepeate rules define pananum

